  "openapi": "3.0.0",
  "info": {
    "x-ibm-name": "tracking-api",
    "title": "Tracking API",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "This API allow customers to track TCS shipments, It's easy to track your shipment online with this API. Simply enter your consignment/shipment number (CN) to get same details provided on the website.\n\n<label>Prerequisites</label>\n\n1. Request parameter key names must be correct (case sensitive).\n2. Input parameter key values are not case sensitive.\n3. Subscription must be made to API product before integration.\n4. Consumers can use their Reference Numbers instead of CN.\n\n<label>Message Status</label>  \n\nReply message status can be determined from below object.\n\n<pre><code>{ \n  \"returnStatus\":    { \n     \"code\": \"0200\", \n     \"status\": \"SUCCESS\", \n     \"message\": \"The operation was successful.\", \n     \"requestTime\": \"20180724111142089\", \n     \"responseTime\": \"20180724111143100\"\n  }  \n}</code></pre>\n\n| Code | Description |\n| ------ | ------ |\n| 0200 | The operation was successful. |\n| 0400 | Bad Request / Custom validation message. |\n| 0404 | Data Not Found. |\n| 0408 | The server is taking too long to respond, please try later. |\n| 0500 | An internal error has occurred.|\n\n# Authentication\n\n<!-- ReDoc-Inject: <security-definitions> -->"
  },
